T02TD2682E:197b-24: // / da ni byang shar mtshams kyi khro bo takki r'a dza'i don rgyas par ston te ;

T02TD2682E:197b-27: las thams cad byed du 'jug par gsungs zhes pa'i bar ni //
T02TD2682E:197b-28: 'dod khams kyi sems can gyi gzung ba dang /

T02TD2682E:198a-1: 'byung bas na 'byung po log pa'i mthu rab tu zhen pas rdzas kyi bye brag sna tshogs pa las 'byung ba dang /
T02TD2682E:198a-2: sngon gyi las las gyur pa'i 'byung po thams cad kyi rgyal po dbang ldan la sogs pa rnams 'gugs par byed pa'i rtags kyi phyag rgya ni 'dul ba'i dbang du sku sprul ste 'gro ba'i don byed pa'i rtags takki r'a dza ste /

T02TD2682E:198a-4: des phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi phrin las sna tshogs pa rab tu mdzad pa thams cad byed du 'jug cing nyams su len pa rnams byams pa'i ral gris mngon du btul te legs par gnas pa'i don to //
T02TD2682E:198a-5: byang shar mtshams kyi khro bo'i rgyal po takki r'a dza'i don rgyas par bshad zin to /
T02TD2682E:198a-7: // / da ni lho nub mtshams kyi khro bo'i rgyal po stobs po che'i don rgyas par bshad de /

T02TD2682E:198a-10: de ni ma grub pa rnams grub par byed pa /
T02TD2682E:198a-11: 'dod pa thams cad rab tu sbyin pa zhes pa dang /
T02TD2682E:198a-12: khro bo'i rgyal po stobs po cher bstan zhes pa'i bar ni rnal 'byor sgrub pa po gang yang rung ba dag gis 'di tshul bzhin du bsgrubs na mdo las 'byung ba'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub ma grub pa rnams grub par byed pa /
T02TD2682E:198a-13: sgrub par byed pa'i thabs rnam par sna tshogs pa'i las rnam pas kyi rgol ba bdud ram pa bzhi nyon mongs pa dang phung bo dang lha'i bu dang 'chi bdag gi bdud rnams kyi dbang du mi gtong bar mdzad pa dang /
T02TD2682E:198a-14: de bzhin gshegs pa'i yon tan gyi rnam grangs ma lus pa thams cad rab tu sbyin par mdzad par dang dpa' bar 'gro bdag zla ba'i rgyal mtshan la sogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i stobs dang ldan pa /
T02TD2682E:198a-15: 'jig rten gyi khams kyi sems can gyi 'dod pa phun sum tshogs pa rnam pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa rnams thob par sgrub cing de bzhin gshegs pa'i phrin las sna tshogs pa mdzad do //
T02TD2682E:198a-16: lho nub mtshams kyi khro bo'i rgyal po stobs po che'i don rgyas par bshad zin to /
T02TD2682E:198a-18: // / da ni nub byang mtshams kyi khro bo aa mo gha p'a sha'i don ston te /

T02TD2682E:199a-1: la 'jigs byed thabs la mkhas pa'i sprul pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa rnam pa sna tshogs pa dang gis gnod par byed pa'i sems can gzhan la bsnan nas /

T02TD2682E:199b-0: rmugs @199b par byed pa'i gsang sngags kyi mthu chen po 'di zhes pa dang /

T02TD2682E:200a-6: mi dang mi ma yin pa rnams su lag na rdo rjer so sor skad du 'ur ces rab tu gyur pa'i don to //

T02TD2682E:210b-35: gzhan du na dkyil 'khor gyi zhal kha ba dang /
T02TD2682E:210b-38: bum pa'i don sbyar ba bshad zin to /
T02TD2682E:210b-40: // / da ni grangs kyi khyad par gyi don ston te /
T02TD2682E:210b-41: da ni bzlas brjod kyi don la dga' ba'i dbang du gsungs te /
T02TD2682E:210b-42: lan grangs nyi shu rtsa gcig gam //
T02TD2682E:210b-43: yang na lan grangs brgya rtsa brgyad //
T02TD2682E:211a-3: 'bangs nyi shu rtsa gcig la sogs te /
T02TD2682E:211a-4: ci 'byor pa blon po ni brgya rtsa brgyad la sogs te 'grub tshad do //
T02TD2682E:211a-5: rgyal po ni bsod nams che bas tha ma brgya rtsa brgyad do //
T02TD2682E:211a-6: blon po tha ma nyi shu rtsa gcig /'bangs kyi tha ma bdun no //
T02TD2682E:211a-7: da ni grangs kyi bsnyen pa'i don /
T02TD2682E:211a-12: rang bzhin gyis shes par bya ba'i tha tshig go zhes pa ni /
T02TD2682E:211a-13: grangs kyi bsnyen pa'i don dang /
T02TD2682E:211a-14: dus kyi bsnyen pa'i don dang ldan pa ste /
T02TD2682E:211a-15: de yang bzlas brjod la dga' ba dang /
T02TD2682E:211a-16: dngos grub kyi rtags kyi mtshan ma la dga' ba dang /
T02TD2682E:211a-20: skar ma la dga' ba'i don gsungs so //
T02TD2682E:211a-21: de yang bzlas pa'i don la dga' ba la sngags kyi bzlas pa gsungs so //
T02TD2682E:211a-22: don gyi bzlas pa'i ting nge 'dzin la dga' ba'i phyir ro //
T02TD2682E:211a-23: gang gis de'i 'og tu khrus bya ba'i dmigs ni /
T02TD2682E:211a-24: rgyal po rtag tu khrus kyis shig / ces pa'i don ni /
T02TD2682E:211a-25: rgyal po stobs ldan snying po la sogs pa /
T02TD2682E:211a-26: rgyal po'i rigs su gtogs pa rnams so zhes pa dang /
T02TD2682E:211a-27: don gyis shes par bya ba'i tha tshig tu rig par bya'o zhes pa'i bar ni /
T02TD2682E:211a-28: mdo'i don ni sems can thams cad byang chub snying po can du byin gyis brlabs pa'i phyir na /
T02TD2682E:211a-29: sems can gyi dpon po rgyal po smos pas na /
T02TD2682E:211a-30: phyi rabs kyi 'gro ba'i dpon po rgyal po bas gtsor byas pas na /
T02TD2682E:211a-32: nang gi khrus bya ba dang /
T02TD2682E:211a-33: phyi nang gnyi ga'i khrus bya'o //
T02TD2682E:211a-35: nang ting nge 'dzin gyi dbang du byas pa ste /
T02TD2682E:211a-38: rnam pa gcig tu phyi lus dang /
T02TD2682E:211a-39: nang sems kyi bag chags kyi rnam pa'o //
T02TD2682E:211a-41: da ni dge ba bsngo ba'i tshul ston te /
T02TD2682E:211a-43: mdo'i don gyis dgongs pa la zhes pa'o //
T02TD2682E:211a-46: brtsams pa dang mi mthun pa ni /
T02TD2682E:211a-47: 'phags pa rnams la bzod par gsol /
T02TD2682E:211a-49: 'di grub brtsams pas bde grub shog / zhes pa dang /
T02TD2682E:211a-50: slob dpon gyis dge ba bsngo ba'i tshul lo //
T02TD2682E:211b-0: 'di don gzhan gyis @211b bshad kyang de gsal phyir /
T02TD2682E:211b-1: gtan tshigs rigs pas mdo yi dgongs pa bkrol //
T02TD2682E:211b-2: mkhas pa rnams kyis mi dpya bzod par gsol //
T02TD2682E:211b-3: bsod nams mi slu 'gro ba yongs la bsngo //
T02TD2682E:211b-4: rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa'i gzungs kyi don rnam par bshad pa rgya cher 'grel pa /
T02TD2682E:211b-5: b'i ma la mi hras mdzad pa rdzogs so//
